---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Reviews" description="See what customers are saying about TrueFix Auto in Colorado Springs. Real Google reviews from real customers.">

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <div class="section-label light">Customer Reviews</div>
      <h1 class="section-title light">DON'T TAKE<br>OUR WORD FOR IT.</h1>
      <p>Real reviews from real customers in Colorado Springs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rating-badge">
      <div class="rating-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <div class="rating-num">5.0</div>
      <div class="rating-source">on Google Reviews</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- REVIEWS GRID -->
  <section class="reviews-section">

    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I’m was new in the area about a year ago when I stopped by they took their time to explain and went above and beyond for my vehicle. Very honest and fair prices. Ever since they have always been friendly. If I have an issue I stop and cowboy always makes time to help, it may not get fixed that day but I know they’ll get it done and always in very fair and honest manner. Thank you guys so very much for taking care of my family’s vehicle."</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Anahi Rodriguez</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I’ve been coming to Cowboy Mechanic Shop for about 10 months now, and every visit has been nothing but great. I recently brought my truck in for a tune-up, and the service was top-notch, fast, honest, and professional. These guys really know what they’re doing, and you can tell they take pride in their work. I’m also excited to try their new car detailing service when it launches. If you’re looking for a mechanic you can trust, Cowboy is the place to go!"</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Moussa Diao</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I brought in my 2003 Buick lesabre for squeaky brakes and a check engine light. Cowboy (the owner) worked on the car, kept me updated the entire time, and found a coolant leak that needed to be fixed that I didn't know about 😅. very reasonable prices, didn't try and upcharge or anything, and my car was done the same day I brought it in. highly highly recommend!!"</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Eden Mae Yates</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Cowboy Mechanic Shop is fantastic! I was greeted with a smile, given an honest estimate within my budget, and there was no up charging. My car was ready quickly and not stuck in the shop for days. Honest, fast, affordable and veteran-owned. Highly recommend!"</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Anthony Rivera</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Super professional and great communication. They did everything they said they would. Their honest opinion on certain parts I thought may need fixed but they said they'd be fine and pointed out actual priority things instead. I'll definitely recommend them to anybody."</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Camden Burton</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Cowboy serviced my vehicle. I truly and highly recommend coming here. As a woman it is difficult finding honest mechanic, I also really appreciate their fairness in price and they didn’t leave until my vehicle was fixed even though they were extremely busy when I got there. Talked to me in terms I could understand, made a very stressful day easy to deal with. I wish I would’ve found them sooner! Phenomenal service, going back in 2 weeks to get my alignment done and transmission serviced!"</p>
        <div class="review-footer">
          <div class="review-author">Rosheyly Martinez</div>
          <div class="review-meta">Google Review · Verified Customer</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="reviews-see-all">
      <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Cowboys+Mechanic+Shop+Colorado+Springs+Reviews&ludocid=18315268684440215550" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">See All Google Reviews →</a>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--black);
    padding: 72px 80px 60px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .page-header-inner p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.5);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .rating-badge {
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(30,125,52,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,125,52,0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 36px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .rating-stars {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--green-light);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rating-num {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .rating-source {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(245,242,236,0.4);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* REVIEWS */
  .reviews-section {
    padding: 72px 80px;
    background: var(--green-pale);
  }

  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .review-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .review-card.featured { border-left-width: 4px; }
  .review-card.placeholder-card { border-left-color: var(--border); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

  .stars {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .review-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-style: italic;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .placeholder-text {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .review-footer {}
  .review-author {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--black);
  }
  .review-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-top: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .leave-review-link {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .leave-review-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .reviews-see-all {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 48px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header { padding: 48px 24px 40px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 28px; }
    .rating-badge { width: 100%; padding: 20px; }
    .reviews-section { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .google-cta { padding: 48px 24px; }
    .google-cta-inner h2 { font-size: 32px; }
  }
</style>